            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>mozzarella</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tear the <strong>mozzarella</strong> into bite-sized pieces, pat it dry with kitchen paper, pressing down very firmly so that it's really dry</p>\r\n<p>Drain the <strong>tuna</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
