    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated baking tray from the oven and add the <strong>naan breads&nbsp;</strong>(use tin foil to avoid mess!)</p>\r\n<p>Spread the <strong>tomato base</strong> over the <strong>naan breads&nbsp;</strong>with the back of a spoon</p>\r\n<p>Dot the<strong> torn mozzarella</strong> over,&nbsp;followed by the<strong> tuna</strong> and the <strong>sliced olives</strong></p>",
